caption.p: Effect of Cuminum cyminum seed essential oil on hatching of M. incognita and M. javanica J2s after immersion in test solutions at concentrations of 0, 7.8, 15.6, 31.2, 62.5, 125, 250, and 500 μL/L for 35 days. * Bars with the same color followed by the same letter are not significantly different according to Tukey’s HSD test at p < 0.05.
